cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.AI 

This paper focuses on the optimization of UAV trajectories for wireless communication systems, which involves network infrastructure and control. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization of UAV movement, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also considers the impact of user mobility, which involves system dynamics and control, and thus falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper proposes a distributed algorithm for trajectory design, which involves game theory and decision-making, and thus falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
